{ The minority attack is a common plan for Black in the Carlsbad structure. This is a typical way to activate your pieces and make use of the open lines not only for the Carlsbad structure/London System, but in general @@StartBracket@@the pawn structure doesn't have to be literally the same@@EndBracket@@, but here we get to see it in the purest form. }
11... Rab8
