9. Ne5
{ This move is very unpleasant for Black! Surprisingly enough, Black is still relatively okay after  9...Qc8  where I recommend  10.Bd3  with an easier game for White, but according to the stats ➼ most of the players will fall for the trap. }
9... Nxe5 { Eliminating the annoying knight seems logical right? } 10. dxe5
{ After this important move White wins at least a piece. } 10... Ne4 11. Bb5
{ Winning Black's queen. } *

