[White "Typical Pawn Structures"]
[Black "Introduction"]
[Result "*"]

{ This section is a mix of the most common London System pawn structures that we can get. The goal of it is to familiarize you with the main plans for both sides in less than 15 minutes. To get a deeper understanding you can have a look at the games that are linked in each chapter! }
1. -- *

