10... Nf6 11. Bb5
{ This is not really planning to play Bxc6 directly, but combined with Nf3 ➼ Black will have issues with the e5-bishop. }
11... O-O 12. O-O
{ With a concrete threat of playing Nf3 and White is completely winning. } *

