{ This move has a crushing winrate while being the engine's top choice. The idea is to push f3 followed by g4 ➼ hunting the h5-bishop. }
5... h6 { This move is important, but not an easy find. } 6. f3
{ Preparing to push g4. } 6... Nfd7
{ This is the only important line. Everything else allows g4 followed by Nxg6 with similar positions to what we've seen in the 5...e6 line. }
