7. Nc3 Be7
{ This is a clever move order, with the idea to castle short next, avoiding the quick disaster after cxd5 followed by Nb5. Jobava is the strongest player that uses this trick. }
8. Rc1 O-O 9. cxd5
{ Even though we won't get a quick win in this line, White still keeps a pleasant position. }
9... Nxd5
