8. Rc1
{ This line has an insane potential to give you a quick win according to my experience and what people do on average in the database. Even strong players have failed to avoid the upcoming deadly traps.   In case you are a fan of slower play, there is a good alternative in going  8.h3  followed by Be2 and O-O with a pleasant position. }
