6... Qb6
{ Offering the queen trade. This is the main line in OTB games, and also what I have encountered the most in online chess.   6...Bxb1?  , intending to meet  7.Rxb1  with  7...Qa5+  , doesn't work due to the strong intermezzo  7.Qxb7!  when White just wins, as after  7...Qa5+  8.Kd1+-  White will collect the rook on a8 on the next move. }
