13... Qd7 14. Kg2
{ White's king has reached safety while Black's king is stuck in the middle of the board! }
14... Rc8 15. h4
{ Threatening to expand further with h5, White won a model game in Kravtsiv,M  @@StartBracket@@2628@@EndBracket@@-Mchedlishvili,M @@StartBracket@@2571@@EndBracket@@ Konya 2019. }
