10. a3 Na6
{ In case of  10...Nc6  the move  11.Nb3  attacks Black's queen and wins the d5-pawn on the next move. Now one game continued  11...Qb6  12.cxd5  Nb8  13.Rc1  Bd7  14.Ne5±  and Black was under a lot of pressure in the game between Romero Pallares,D @@StartBracket@@2170@@EndBracket@@-Santos Ruiz,M @@StartBracket@@2594@@EndBracket@@ Benasque 2021. }
11. cxd5
{ Improving over Rosen's game that went  11.Ne5  with an unclear game. After  11.cxd5  Black has problems developing. }
11... e6 12. Ne5 { With Qa4 ideas looming, Black is in trouble. } *

