6... Bb7 7. e4 b5
{ The computer is a huge fan of White's position generally, but it's incredibly tricky to play. If you can manage these type of positions, by all means go for it, but from personal experience, it's much easier to play as Black here. }
8. Qe2
{ This is very important, preparing O-O-O and intending to meet  8...b4  with  9.Na4! }
