{ Threatening to play c4 followed by Bc3 ➼ trapping Black's queen. } 9... Na6
10. Rb1
{ This is important because the immediate  10.c4  would have allowed  10...Ndb4  ideas. }
10... Qa2 11. c4 { Attacking the d5-knight. } 11... Nf6 12. Ra1
{ Forcing the queen back to b2 where we can trap it. } 12... Qb2 13. Bc3
{ Collecting Black's queen on the next move. } *

