{ After you have mastered the Thematic Puzzles, this chapter will mix very well with it. Once you get a general understanding of the Theory Chapters and you have gone through the Thematic Puzzles, you are already a very dangerous London System player, but this chapter ➼ will synergize everything really well.   Sometimes just getting the theory right won't put you in such a big lead in order to create a tactical opportunity, but if you also apply the thematic maneuvers, most of the time there will be a tactical shot that allows you to win the game @@StartBracket@@or squeeze them into the endgame, that's also fine!@@EndBracket@@. }
