[White "Reference Games"]
[Black "Introduction"]
[Result "*"]

{ In an effort to showcase to students both many potential move orders through which some typical London positions arise, and the middlegame and endgame plans that follow those positions, the annotations of this course include many references to full games.   I selected 31 of the most instructive of these games and annotated them in full in the Model Games chapter, and I included a further 21 games in the Typical Endgames chapter with the endgame part of those games annotated.   This Reference Games chapter includes all other games referenced throughout the course, so that students can look them up conveniently even without access to additional databases. }
