[White "Reference Games"]
[Black "Brunello, Sabino vs. De Ruiter, Danny, 2016"]
[Result "*"]

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 d5 3. Bf4 Bf5 4. e3 c6 5. Bd3 Bg6 6. O-O e6 7. Ne5 Nbd7 8.
